{"tid":578392,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】開台前輸到心情極差可如何處理? Day179 2/3","createTime":"2018-03-02T14:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T17:31:57.000Z","uid":122942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5c58f107241398c6ba1a88f3a7316220d0ebcd","tid":578392,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bad16613\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=014a0ce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"a3f368576876424bca10790e9441c43c71930af0","tid":578392,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bac7ca203affbfeffcb132b0fed92aaf6c545e","tid":578392,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3873a48c5cbc7bb5cbf98660ced8979ad069f5c7","tid":57839